{"tid":1501184,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急任】要求反對前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名","createTime":"2019-08-24T09:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T23:03:45.000Z","uid":80630,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9cbc66404f926b6d4d5ec7023535605282fe50","tid":1501184,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"Hi又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼將共產黨列為恐怖組織聯署之後<br />\n唔該大家簽簽呢個聯署<br />\n<br />\n【緊急呼籲】<br />\n<br />\n要求反對前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Z0cMkw&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=5ef8ff5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw</a></strong></span><br />\n簽名＞等電郵＞<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>確認簽名</strong></span>＞傳開去<br />\n<br />\n呢個遠遠唔夠數，可能大家已經唔記得邊個係曾偉雄？<br />\n香港搞到今時今日咁，佢一定係罪魁禍首之一。<br />\n想印印腳去聯合國高薪厚職？<br />\n大家做啲嘢啦！"},{"pid":"7d6d561add8e4fa7208455a9208c3c64a857bbf8","tid":1501184,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:39:35.000Z","msg":"［聯署］唔怪得將共產黨列為恐怖組織呢個簽極都仲咁少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1493343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1493343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9cb2a715817db4e779f83fbc3dae810cc5293fa0","tid":1501184,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2cdd1c97952f4ab7a84b74be80050d8bfb0497e8","tid":1501184,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:42:37.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知有無用  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class